<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbc9f988a-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s3940"><num value="3940">§ 3940.</num><heading> Reservation of right to repeal, alter, or amend chapter</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The right to repeal, alter, or amend this chapter at any time is expressly reserved.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbc9f988b-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/90/448/tIX/s910">Pub. L. 90–448, title IX, § 910</ref>, <date date="1968-08-01">Aug. 1, 1968</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/82/550">82 Stat. 550</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
